tude band, similar to that simulated by several$\backslash$ncoupled models. We suggest that if ENSO is not adequately resolved in$\backslash$ncoupled models but structures with zonal wavenumber 3 pattern are, then$\backslash$nthe modeled ACW would appear to have a zonal wavenumber 3 pattern.},
